{"tid":2026652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普：中國發言人愚蠢...","createTime":"2020-05-21T05:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T06:26:45.000Z","uid":30561,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"315baf9c45741365c0219d7c93e04df45bb3bf31","tid":2026652,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:54:42.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）全球大流行，已造成32多萬人喪命。美國總統川普今天點名中國發言人，直指對方愚蠢代表中國說話，進行一場大規模假訊息宣傳戰。川普疑似在回應中國外交部發言人趙立堅20日的言論。<br />\n<br />\n川普今天在推特上表示，發言人愚蠢地代表中國說話，拚命試圖轉移中國在全世界蔓延的痛苦和屠殺，中國對美國和歐洲的假訊息宣傳攻擊是一種恥辱，而這一切都來自中國高層，中國本來可以輕易阻止疫情，但中國沒有做到。<br />\n<br />\n川普強調，中國正在進行一場大規模的假宣傳活動，因為中方迫切希望民主黨總統參選人拜登（Joe Biden）贏得總統選舉，這樣中方就可以像過去十幾年以來繼續剝削美國。<br />\n<br />\n川普20日也曾透過推特痛罵中國，「中國有個瘋子剛發表聲明，為病毒怪東怪西就是不怪中國自己，現在疫情已奪走數十萬條人命。請跟這個笨蛋解釋，造成全球大屠殺的就是『中國的無能』，沒有其他原因了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/05/21/nOEMG2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F05%2F21%2FnOEMG2.png&h=658f7b12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n趙立堅20日在中國外交部例行記者會，被問到川普致世界衛生組織（WHO）秘書長譚德塞的信，以及中國如何看待加拿大、歐盟、俄羅斯的反應。趙立堅表示，國際社會對美方這種歪曲事實、自相矛盾、嫁禍於人、甩鍋推責、破壞國際抗疫合作的行徑普遍不認同，美方這封信羅列的那些謬誤，中方已經澄清並駁斥多次，世人的眼睛是雪亮的，這封信的可信度到底有多高，國際社會自有公論。"},{"pid":"cb84455f6cc4d88d0149f6ce7ef9123cbf27d08f","tid":2026652,"uid":59898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />侵仔<br />\n人類既希望"},{"pid":"f5c4c00f3f4ffa4cb852b0f99c6edcadad040ad3","tid":2026652,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:56:24.000Z","msg":"阻阻你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入嚟幫下手足 或者推下po<br />\n<br />\n［召喚寫信師］荔枝角在囚手足有事請大家幫忙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2026624\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2026624</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"324e9b292eab419a06a0b8deba9f97a3d4670cb4","tid":2026652,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實自有記憶以來都愚蠢  但唔知點解要到2020年今日先有人指出E個問題出黎"},{"pid":"65743f07062de2356edb29278b074a0508748d64","tid":2026652,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:06:40.000Z","msg":"係咪屌緊爽爽同華大媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7738c7057e29ffe1c59e8a91b45506e2e731b5ca","tid":2026652,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65743f07062de2356edb29278b074a0508748d64","tid":2026652,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:06:40.000Z","msg":"係咪屌緊爽爽同華大媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:08:05.000Z","msg":"堅堅似係最發力既一位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65be6f5a23c3f34fc727701df380717d9bc896f8","tid":2026652,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:21:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">既然已經認清鬼國本質，那趕緊行動！ ！ ！別再等了，再拖全世界因鬼國而死於非命的人就越多！鬼國納粹70年的滔天罪行難道還不足以喚醒世界各國嗎？ ！</span>"},{"pid":"4980ac7f1389789bc4e117210ab71cf0d4048a02","tid":2026652,"uid":114014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T